contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|HDF}} '''HDF''' may refer to: * [[Hadfield railway station]] (National Rail station code), in Derbyshire, England * [[Heringsdorf Airport]], (IATA airport code), near Garz on the island of Usedom, Germany * [[Hierarchical Data Format]], file formats and libraries for storing numerical data * [[High-density fiberboard]], an engineered wood product * [[Hubble Deep Field]], an image of a small region in the constellation Ursa Major * [[Human Development Foundation]], an organization in Bangkok, Thailand {{disambiguation}}
